node.title: Cyclist dies after crash in Te Aroha
node.description: A cyclist has died following a crash in Te Aroha, in Waikato.
node.content:
["A cyclist has died following a crash in Te Aroha, in Waikato.", "", "
\nPhoto: 123RF\n
", "Emergency services were called at 11am to the intersection of Waiorongomai Road and Te Aroha-Gordon Road.", "The crash involved the cyclist and a car.", "The road is expected to re-open soon, a police spokesperson said.", "Another cyclist was seriously injured in a crash with a bus in the Auckland suburb of \u014ctara on Tuesday evening."]
